        <span class="alliance-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        <div><small>Representative members</small><p>Delta · Air France · KLM · Aeromexico</p></div>
        <span class="alliance-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        <div><small>Major U.S. hubs</small><p class="hub-codes"><b>ATL</b><b>JFK</b><b>DTW</b><b>MSP</b></p></div>
      </article>
